trans-unit.source: Connects an ActiveX control to a client that handles the control’s events.
trans-unit.target: Conecta um controle ActiveX a um cliente que trata os eventos do controle.

trans-unit.source: ActiveX controls communicate with clients through their COM interface.
trans-unit.target: Controles ActiveX se comunicar com clientes por meio de sua interface COM.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost.ConnectionPointCookie> class provides the link between the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost> class and the ActiveX control.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost.ConnectionPointCookie> classe fornece o vínculo entre o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost> classe e o controle ActiveX.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see "Events in COM and Connectable Objects" in the MSDN library at http://msdn.microsoft.com/library.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte "Eventos no e conectável objetos COM" na biblioteca MSDN em http://msdn.microsoft.com/library.

trans-unit.source: A connectable object that contains connection points.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto conectável que contém pontos de conexão.

trans-unit.source: The client's sink which receives outgoing calls from the connection point.
trans-unit.target: O coletor do cliente que recebe chamadas de saída do ponto de conexão.

trans-unit.source: The outgoing interface whose connection point object is being requested.
trans-unit.target: A interface de saída cujo objeto de ponto de conexão está sendo solicitado.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost.ConnectionPointCookie" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost.ConnectionPointCookie" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost.ConnectionPointCookie.%23ctor%2A> constructor establishes a connection between the ActiveX control and the client.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost.ConnectionPointCookie.%23ctor%2A> construtor estabelece uma conexão entre o cliente e o controle ActiveX.

trans-unit.source: The connection point has already reached its limit of connections and cannot accept any more.
trans-unit.target: O ponto de conexão já atingiu seu limite de conexões e não pode aceitar mais nenhuma.

trans-unit.source: Disconnects the ActiveX control from the client.
trans-unit.target: Desconecta o controle ActiveX do cliente.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost.ConnectionPointCookie" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Libera os recursos não gerenciados usados pela classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost.ConnectionPointCookie" />.

trans-unit.source: Application code should not call this method; an object's `Finalize` method is automatically invoked during garbage collection, unless finalization by the garbage collector has been disabled by a call to the <xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: O código do aplicativo não deve chamar este método; o método `Finalize` de um objeto é invocado automaticamente durante a coleta de lixo, a menos que a finalização pelo coletor de lixo tenha sido desabilitada por uma chamada para o método <xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%2A>.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Finalize Methods and Destructors](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/fd376774-1643-499b-869e-9546a3aeea70), [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md), and [Overriding the Finalize Method](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [métodos Finalize e destruidores](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/fd376774-1643-499b-869e-9546a3aeea70), [limpeza de recursos não gerenciados](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md), e [substituindo o método Finalize](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3).
